sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant Gateway
    participant AI as algoshare-ai
    participant Order as algoshare-order
    participant LLM as External AI

    Client->>Gateway: POST /api/ai/chat "Why did trade #123 fail?"
    Gateway->>Gateway: Rate Limit Check
    Gateway->>AI: Forward Request

    AI->>Order: GET /orders/123 (Fetch details)
    Order-->>AI: {status: REJECTED, reason: No Funds}

    AI->>LLM: Generate Explanation
    LLM-->>AI: "The trade failed due to insufficient balance..."
    AI-->>Client: 200 OK + Explanation